Icyakora, guhera mu mwaka wa 2013 Afurika yari umugabane w’iterambere ryihuse ku isi ku kigero cya 5,6% ku mwaka, kandi biteganijwe ko GDP iziyongera ku kigereranyo cya 6% ku mwaka hagati ya 2013 na 2023.<ref>[[Oliver August (2 March 2013). "Africa rising A hopeful continent". The Economist. The Economist Newspaper Limited. Retrieved 15 December 2013.]]</ref> Muri 2017, Banki Nyafurika itsura amajyambere yatangaje ko Afurika ari iya kabiri ku isi ifite ubukungu bwihuta cyane, inavuga ko ubukungu buziyongera kugera kuri 3,4% muri 2017, mu gihe biteganijwe ko izamuka rizagera kuri 4.3% muri 2018.<ref>[["African Economic Outlook 2017" (PDF). African Development Bank.]]</ref> Ubwiyongere bwagaragaye ku mugabane wa Afurika, aho kimwe cya gatatu cy’ibihugu bya Afurika byagaragaje kwiyongera kw' iterambere  ku kigereranyo cya 6%  kuzamura, naho 40% byiyongera hagati ya 4% kugeza 6% kumwaka. Indorerezi mpuzamahanga z’ubucuruzi nazo zise Afurika nk’imoteri izamura ubukungu ku isi.<ref>[["Rise of the African opportunity". Boston Analytics. 22 June 2016.]]</ref>

== Amateka ==
[[File:Coudée-turin.jpg|right|thumb|300x300px|ibipimo fatizo  bya Misiri Ya kera byanakoreshwaga nkifaranga ryabo]]
Ubukungu bwa Afurika bwari butandukanye, ahanini bwari bushingiye ku nzira nini z'ubucuruzi zari zarakozwe hagati y'imijyi n'ubwami. Inzira zimwe z'ubucuruzi zanyuraga ku  butaka, izindi zikanyura mu nzuzi, izindi zo mu bihugu byateye imbere zanyuraga ku byambu bikikije imigi. Ubwami bunini bw'Afurika bwagiye bukira kubera imiyoboro y’ubucuruzi bwari bufite, urugero nka Misiri ya kera, Nubiya, [[Mali]], Ashanti, n’ubwami bwa Oyo .
[[File:Mogadishan_currency.JPG|left|thumb|359x359px|Soltanate yifaranga rya Mogadishu .]]
Bimwe mu bice bya Afurika byari bifitanye umubano w’ubucuruzi n’ubwami bw’abarabu, kandi mu gihe cy’ingoma ya Ottoman, Abanyafurika batangiye kwinjira mu idini rya Isilamu ari benshi. Iterambere, hamwe nubushobozi bwubukungu mugushakisha inzira yubucuruzi igana inyanja yu Buhinde, byazanye Abanyaportigale muri Afrika yo munsi y’ubutayu bwa Sahara nkingabo zifite ingufu z’ubwami. Kubw'Inyungu zabakoloni bashizeho inganda nshya zo kugaburira ibyifuzo by’i Burayi ku bicuruzwa nk’amavuta y’amamesa, reberi, ipamba, ibyuma byagaciro, ibirungo, ibihingwa ngengabukungu ibindi bicuruzwa, kandi bahuza cyane cyane uturere two ku nkombe n’ubukungu bwa Atlantike. 

Nyuma y’ubwigenge bw’ibihugu bya Afurika mu kinyejana cya 20, imidugararo mu bukungu, muri politiki ndetse no mu mibereho byahungabanije cyane umugabane. Ariko mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe ubukungu bwarazamutse  bigaragara, mu myaka yashize. 
